Welcome to G-Guava!

  G-Guava is a small collection of reusable tools for <Google Guice> to make
  easier the integration with {{{Google Guava}http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/}}.

Before starting

  G-Guava is available on the Maven Central repo, you just need to add the dependency below in your <<<pom.xml>>> file:

+--------------------------------------+
<dependencies>
  ...
  <dependency>
    <groupId>${project.groupId}</groupId>
    <artifactId>${project.artifactId}</artifactId>
    <version>${project.version}</version>
  </dependency>
  ...
</dependencies>
+--------------------------------------+

